d":"digging","count":1},{"word":"academy's","count":1},{"word":"mechs","count":1},{"word":"voidmatter","count":1},{"word":"barrier","count":1},{"word":"security","count":1},{"word":"logs","count":1},{"word":"show","count":1},{"word":"unusual","count":1},{"word":"admin-level","count":1},{"word":"protocols","count":1},{"word":"device's","count":1},{"word":"unrecognizable","count":1},{"word":"um","count":1},{"word":"browsing","count":1},{"word":"forum","count":1},{"word":"mm","count":1},{"word":"tasked","count":1},{"word":"hack","count":1},{"word":"institute's","count":1},{"word":"tamper","count":1},{"word":"calibration","count":1},{"word":"change","count":1},{"word":"anything","count":1},{"word":"threw","count":1},{"word":"emojis","count":1},{"word":"left","count":1},{"word":"note","count":1},{"word":"telling","count":1},{"word":"encryption","count":1},{"word":"backfired","count":1},{"word":"though","count":1},{"word":"flagged","count":1},{"word":"next","count":1},{"word":"correspond","count":1},{"word":"clue","count":1},{"word":"ecological","count":1},{"word":"studies","count":1},{"word":"head","count":1},{"word":"spacetrek","count":1},{"word":"archive","count":1},{"word":"allow","count":1},{"word":"introduce","count":1},{"word":"archive's","count":1},{"word":"administrator","count":1},{"word":"responsible","count":1},{"word":"indexing","count":1},{"word":"reliable","count":1},{"word":"beat","count":1},{"word":"info","count":1},{"word":"related","count":1},{"word":"waveform","count":1},{"word":"lot","count":1},{"word":"keywords","count":1},{"word":"contamination","count":1},{"word":"big","count":1},{"word":"improvement","count":1},{"word":"split","count":1},{"word":"review","count":1},{"word":"whew","count":1},{"word":"goodness","count":1},{"word":"whoa","count":1},{"word":"many","count":1},{"word":"dark","count":1},{"word":"thunderbolt","count":1},{"word":"report","count":1},{"word":"anymore","count":1},{"word":"return","count":1},{"word":"inquiry","count":1},{"word":"problem","count":1},{"word":"gosh","count":1},{"word":"i'd","count":1},{"word":"happy","count":1},{"word":"freaking","count":1},{"word":"convenience","count":1},{"word":"store's","count":1},{"word":"specials","count":1},{"word":"become","count":1},{"word":"freshman","count":1},{"word":"grab","count":1},{"word":"bite","count":1},{"word":"together","count":1},{"word":"testify","count":1},{"word":"perjury","count":1},{"word":"verbal","count":1},{"word":"magic","count":1},{"word":"dealing","count":1},{"word":"side","count":1},{"word":"working","count":1}],"lines":[{"text":"{PlayerName}—over here!","quest_name":"Ode to the Second Sunrise","quest_id":155000002},{"text":"You bet! Just passed all my entrance exams yesterday!","quest_name":"Ode to the Second Sunrise","quest_id":155000002},{"text":"Which means... today you're officially meeting \"Lynae, first-year student in Startorch Academy\"!","quest_name":"Ode to the Second Sunrise","quest_id":155000002},{"text":"Ugh, I really wanna hit the road with you again, but I'm kinda on a \"mental health watchlist.\" If I break even one tiny rule on day one, Miss Lucilla will be dragging me in for a \"friendly chat.\"","quest_name":"Ode to the Second Sunrise","quest_id":155000002},{"text":"I gotta hold out until I figure out a route that slips past the cameras.","quest_name":"Ode to the Second Sunrise","quest_id":155000002},{"text":"Oh, but hey, you got Mornye's email about the <te href=700013>Hyvatia Detector</te>, right? It's almost go-time. How about we hang by the entrance, and then we—","quest_name":"Ode to the Second Sunrise","quest_id":155000002},{"text":"Ah, haha! Not at all. Actually, you noticed us right as the clock struck the hour. Perfect timing, Professor.","quest_name":"Ode to the Second Sunrise","quest_id":155000002},{"text":"Of course, come on in. I already tidied up my dorm, so sit wherever you like!","quest_name":"Ode to the Second Sunrise","quest_id":155000002},{"text":"So it's true, huh? You guys actually made food that tastes awful but keeps you running for three days straight. I thought that was just a joke.","quest_name":"Ode to the Second Sunrise","quest_id":155000002},{"text":"Uh... Professor Mornye, you're not here to...","quest_name":"Ode to the Second Sunrise","quest_id":155000002},{"text":"I mean, it all happened really fast! We didn't have any other way to stop it!","quest_name":"Ode to the Second Sunrise","quest_id":155000002},{"text":"Besides, we're just students! We couldn't afford that even if we wanted to...","quest_name":"Ode to the Second Sunrise","quest_id":155000002},{"text":"Pfft... Even Professor Mornye isn't safe from TARD-E's wrath, huh?","quest_name":"Ode to the Second Sunrise","quest_id":155000002},{"text":"No worries, I got this. I'll draw its attention while you two make for it.","quest_name":"Ode to the Second Sunrise","quest_id":155000002},{"text":"Three, two, one—","quest_name":"Ode to the Second Sunrise","quest_id":155000002},{"text":"Professor Mornye, how are you feeling now?","quest_name":"Ode to the Second Sunrise","quest_id":155000003},{"text":"Dr. Herssen said you were in bad shape. It's great to see you've recovered a little.","quest_name":"Ode to the Second Sunrise","quest_id":155000003},{"text":"{PlayerName}? {PlayerName}—Hey, stop spacing out!","quest_name":"Ode to the Second Sunrise","quest_id":155000003},{"text":"To celebrate Professor Mornye waking up and the crisis being averted, don't you think we should...","quest_name":"Ode to the Second Sunrise","quest_id":155000003},{"text":"Go for a ride!","quest_name":"Ode to the Second Sunrise","quest_id":155000003},{"text":"Nothing beats the wind on your face, especially when—","quest_name":"Ode to the Second Sunrise","quest_id":155000003},{"text":"The three of us still don't have a group picture!","quest_name":"Ode to the Second Sunrise","quest_id":155000003},{"text":"So? Not bad, huh?","quest_name":"Ode to the Second Sunrise","quest_id":155000003},{"text":"Back in the day, whenever I was stressed about the future, hanging out here always made me feel a little better.","quest_name":"Ode to the Second Sunrise","quest_id":155000003},{"text":"Look, now we can just enjoy the breeze without a care in the world!","quest_name":"Ode to the Second Sunrise","quest_id":155000003},{"text":"Well, let's scream that from the rooftops!","quest_name":"Ode to the Second Sunrise","quest_id":155000003},{"text":"To freedom!","quest_name":"Ode to the Second Sunrise","quest_id":155000003},{"text":"Mr. S.I.G.M.A.! I've brought the Ninth Great Mystery to pick up {Male=his;Female=her} vehicle.","quest_name":"What Burns Beneath Frostlands","quest_id":915000001},{"text":"Huh? That's it? Pretty underwhelming intro today.","quest_name":"What Burns Beneath Frostlands","quest_id":915000001},{"text":"AHEM! Mr. S.I.G.M.A., we're here for the new student's ride. We need to get to the Research Institute for Cassette burning. Top priority, you know.","quest_name":"What Burns Beneath Frostlands","quest_id":915000001},{"text":"Great. Let's go!","quest_name":"What Burns Beneath Frostlands","quest_id":915000001},{"text":"Ahem, Mr. S.I.G.M.A, all I did was add a turbocharger, tweak the suspension, and upgrade the brakes. Hardly a violation, wouldn't you say?","quest_name":"What Burns Beneath Frostlands","quest_id":915000001},{"text":"Besides, compared to seniors strapping missiles and anti-gravity wheels on, I'm practically a model student.","quest_name":"What Burns Beneath Frostlands","quest_id":915000001},{"text":"Yep. One senior even turned his bike into a light tank for a project. Drove it straight into an active Voidworm zone.","quest_name":"What Burns Beneath Frostlands","quest_id":915000001},{"text":"...Which was revoked when he brought back critical Voidworm data.","quest_name":"What Burns Beneath Frostlands","quest_id":915000001},{"text":"Now's our chance. Go, go!","quest_name":"What Burns Beneath Frostlands","quest_id":915000001},{"text":"I was escorting {PlayerName} to burn {Male=his;Female=her} Cassette at the Institute.","quest_name":"What Burns Beneath Frostlands","quest_id":915000003},{"text":"On my way back to the Academy, I noticed abnormal frequency spikes and contaminated Exoswarm near Sundermere.","quest_name":"What Burns Beneath Frostlands","quest_id":915000003},{"text":"Before I could act, I was surrounded. I tried to contact the Academy, but the Void Storm blocked communications.","quest_name":"What Burns Beneath Frostlands","quest_id":915000003},{"text":"Exoswarm remains should still be there. I assume... you are already investigating them?","quest_name":"What Burns Beneath Frostlands","quest_id":915000003},{"text":"That was quick.","quest_name":"What Burns Beneath Frostlands","quest_id":915000003},{"text":"What about the surveillance cameras? They're equipped to handle Void Storm interference. They should've captured the Exoswarm before things escalated.","quest_name":"What Burns Beneath Frostlands","quest_id":915000003},{"text":"...No.","quest_name":"What Burns Beneath Frostlands","quest_id":915000003},{"text":"What do you mean?","quest_name":"What Burns Beneath Frostlands","quest_id":915000003},{"text":"Thanks for asking, Professor. I keep in touch with my parents whenever I can. If you're implying I have some secret agenda, you'll be disappointed.","quest_name":"What Burns Beneath Frostlands","quest_id":915000003},{"text":"I don't think that's something you should concern yourself with, Professor.","quest_name":"What Burns Beneath Frostlands","quest_id":915000003},{"text":"Phew...","quest_name":"What Burns Beneath Frostlands","quest_id":915000003},{"text":"Thanks… for speaking up for me.","quest_name":"What Burns Beneath Frostlands","quest_id":915000003},{"text":"Straight to the point, huh? I thought you'd let it slide, like they did.","quest_name":"What Burns Beneath Frostlands","quest_id":915000003},{"text":"Good... you're still you.","quest_name":"What Burns Beneath Frostlands","quest_id":915000003},{"text":"Let's talk somewhere else. This place is suffocating.","quest_name":"What Burns Beneath Frostlands","quest_id":915000003},{"text":"({Male=He;Female=She} should've made it to the Institute by now. No danger there... I'll handle this without dragging {Male=him;Female=her} into it.)","quest_name":"What Burns Beneath Frostlands","quest_id":915000003},{"text":"(That message I just got... It's from the Fractsidus \"liaison.\")","quest_name":"What Burns Beneath Frostlands","quest_id":915000003},{"text":"(The Void Storm should've erased him… Yet here I am getting a message from a \"dead\" man.)","quest_name":"What Burns Beneath Frostlands","quest_id":915000003},{"text":"(Someone's using his comms ID. They know what I did, but haven't blown my cover. A threat? Or something else?)","quest_name":"What Burns Beneath Frostlands","quest_id":915000003},{"text":"(Last signal pinged from around here.)","quest_name":"What Burns Beneath Frostlands","quest_id":915000003},{"text":"(Contaminated <te href=700022>Exoswarm</te>?)","quest_name":"What Burns Beneath Frostlands","quest_id":915000003},{"text":"(Better clear them out first.)","quest_name":"What Burns Beneath Frostlands","quest_id":915000003},{"text":"You...!","quest_name":"What Burns Beneath Frostlands","quest_id":915000003},{"text":"Impossible. Who are you really?","quest_name":"What Burns Beneath Frostlands","quest_id":915000003},{"text":"...","quest_name":"What Burns Beneath Frostlands","quest_id":915000003},{"text":"Spare me. Whatever you're planning, I'll stop it.","quest_name":"What Burns Beneath Frostlands","quest_id":915000003},{"text":"Watch out! You have to go!","quest_name":"What Burns Beneath Frostlands","quest_id":915000003},{"text":"The weather's really nice today.","quest_name":"What Burns Beneath Frostlands","quest_id":915000003},{"text":"How do you feel? Settling in alright?","quest_name":"What Burns Beneath Frostlands","quest_id":915000003},{"text":"Yeah. Not bad, huh?","quest_name":"What Burns Beneath Frostlands","quest_id":915000003},{"text":"Heh, I'll take that as a compliment on my driving skills…","quest_name":"What Burns Beneath Frostlands","quest_id":915000003},{"text":"But honestly, it's been ages since I last raced with someone else. Getting to take you for a ride like this? Makes my day!","quest_name":"What Burns Beneath Frostlands","quest_id":915000003},{"text":"Uh-huh. The roar of the engine, wind in my face... It's like I've got my destination and I'm the one calling the shots.","quest_name":"What Burns Beneath Frostlands","quest_id":915000003},{"text":"Look... Lahai-Roi's sky might be artificial, but I found more freedom under it than I've ever known anywhere else.","quest_name":"What Burns Beneath Frostlands","quest_id":915000003},{"text":"Yeah. I mean, you've only got one life, right? Might as well live it the way you want. When to brake, hit the gas. Hell, even the paint job of your ride. Doesn't matter if you're a normie or a Resonator, everyone should have that choice.","quest_name":"What Burns Beneath Frostlands","quest_id":915000003},{"text":"That's what Startorch Academy is to me. Before I came here, I never imagined a place like this could exist. Full of people so pure, so driven...","quest_name":"What Burns Beneath Frostlands","quest_id":915000003},{"text":"With the resolve to burn in the search for answers. With the belief they can actually end the Void Storm and the Threnodian... and maybe break through the Etheric Sea to find what true freedom really looks like.","quest_name":"What Burns Beneath Frostlands","quest_id":915000003},{"text":"It's beautiful, isn't it?","quest_name":"What Burns Beneath Frostlands","quest_id":915000003},{"text":"Watching them chase their dreams… It's hard not to want that for yourself.","quest_name":"What Burns Beneath Frostlands","quest_id":915000003},{"text":"Yeah, you're right.","quest_name":"What Burns Beneath Frostlands","quest_id":915000003},{"text":"…But I've gotta say, things are plenty good enough right now.","quest_name":"What Burns Beneath Frostlands","quest_id":915000003},{"text":"Ah, almost forgot—","quest_name":"What Burns Beneath Frostlands","quest_id":915000003},{"text":"Welcome! You're now officially a Startorch Academy student!","quest_name":"What Burns Beneath Frostlands","quest_id":915000003},{"text":"My first introduction was too rushed, so I'm doing it properly this time. I'm Lynae, a second-year in the Preparatory Program.","quest_name":"What Burns Beneath Frostlands","quest_id":915000003},{"text":"Time flies. Feels like I just got here, and now I'm a second-year. Hehe, you could call me Miss Lynae, if you want.","quest_name":"What Burns Beneath Frostlands","quest_id":915000003},{"text":"...","quest_name":"What Burns Beneath Frostlands","quest_id":915000003},{"text":"Maybe just stick with Lynae, haha. Not really used to the whole formality thing.","quest_name":"What Burns Beneath Frostlands","quest_id":915000003},{"text":"All right, let's get moving! Time to hit the road!","quest_name":"What Burns Beneath Frostlands","quest_id":915000003},{"text":"Ha... this place always brings me peace.","quest_name":"What Burns Beneath Frostlands","quest_id":915000004},{"text":"You want to know who I really am so you can connect the dots on that incident, right?","quest_name":"What Burns Beneath Frostlands","quest_id":915000004},{"text":"I can tell you... but only if you promise me one thing: Let me stay here. At the Academy. As a student.","quest_name":"What Burns Beneath Frostlands","quest_id":915000004},{"text":"...Yeah. More than I can say.","quest_name":"What Burns Beneath Frostlands","quest_id":915000004},{"text":"I'll take your silence as a yes then.","quest_name":"What Burns Beneath Frostlands","quest_id":915000004},{"text":"So, you've heard those old \"pulling a switcheroo\" stories, right?","quest_name":"What Burns Beneath Frostlands","quest_id":915000004},{"text":"Spoiler alert: their mission wasn't completed.","quest_name":"What Burns Beneath Frostlands","quest_id":915000004},{"text":"Professor Warren knows I'm from the New Federation, but not exactly which part.","quest_name":"What Burns Beneath Frostlands","quest_id":915000004},{"text":"It's called the Lawless Zone. Let's just say... you'd see blood spilled every three days, on average. That's where I grew up.","quest_name":"What Burns Beneath Frostlands","quest_id":915000004},{"text":"I had talent, and the New Fed saw it. Put me to work. Off the record. Dirty jobs.","quest_name":"What Burns Beneath Frostlands","quest_id":915000004},{"text":"Then that day happened… It was an accident, but I saw my chance.","quest_name":"What Burns Beneath Frostlands","quest_id":915000004},{"text":"...An admission letter to Lahai-Roi's Startorch Academy.","quest_name":"What Burns Beneath Frostlands","quest_id":915000004},{"text":"I found that recording I played you on the real Lynae's liaison at the Academy.","quest_name":"What Burns Beneath Frostlands","quest_id":915000004},{"text":"So I quickly learned she wasn't just a regular student from the start.","quest_name":"What Burns Beneath Frostlands","quest_id":915000004},{"text":"Even so, I came to Lahai-Roi.","quest_name":"What Burns Beneath Frostlands","quest_id":915000004},{"text":"Everything here… It's nothing like the New Fed. People don't question themselves when they wake up, brush their teeth, and look in the mirror. They just know who they are.","quest_name":"What Burns Beneath Frostlands","quest_id":915000004},{"text":"Look, as far as I'm concerned, the Fractsidus threatens my school life. They're your enemy too.","quest_name":"What Burns Beneath Frostlands","quest_id":915000004},{"text":"We have shared interests. That's a solid basis for us to cooperate.","quest_name":"What Burns Beneath Frostlands","quest_id":915000004},{"text":"...","quest_name":"What Burns Beneath Frostlands","quest_id":915000004},{"text":"Ha... you know, sometimes you really do sound like a teacher.","quest_name":"What Burns Beneath Frostlands","quest_id":915000004},{"text":"Alright then, let me rephrase.","quest_name":"What Burns Beneath Frostlands","quest_id":915000004},{"text":"I like this school. I've met good people here, people who treat me like their friend. People worth protecting.","quest_name":"What Burns Beneath Frostlands","quest_id":915000004},{"text":"That's why I hope you'll help me find out why the Fractsidus are here in Lahai-Roi, {PlayerName}.","quest_name":"What Burns Beneath Frostlands","quest_id":915000004},{"text":"I've been holding in these words forever. Ahh.. Feels good to finally get 'em out.","quest_name":"What Burns Beneath Frostlands","quest_id":915000004},{"text":"As for our first lead...","quest_name":"What Burns Beneath Frostlands","quest_id":915000004},{"text":"What we do know is... Hyvatia's malfunction and the contaminated Exoswarm are definitely connected to this device I found.","quest_name":"What Burns Beneath Frostlands","quest_id":915000004},{"text":"It looks like Academy tech... maybe the Department of Engineering's lab can shed some light.","quest_name":"What Burns Beneath Frostlands","quest_id":915000004},{"text":"Maybe its appearance is just a disguise. Or maybe it means its maker had free access to the Department's resources.","quest_name":"What Burns Beneath Frostlands","quest_id":915000004},{"text":"After all, that \"contact\" who's been feeding me orders might still be inside the Academy.","quest_name":"What Burns Beneath Frostlands","quest_id":915000004},{"text":"If you're ready to start making moves, I know a shortcut.","quest_name":"What Burns Beneath Frostlands","quest_id":915000004},{"text":"Right this way!","quest_name":"What Burns Beneath Frostlands","quest_id":915000004},{"text":"Quick and clean.","quest_name":"What Burns Beneath Frostlands","quest_id":915000004},{"text":"It's been overwritten. Don't have to worry about it being remotely controlled. Glad we pulled it off in time…","quest_name":"What Burns Beneath Frostlands","quest_id":915000004},{"text":"Hah… You got me. It's been a while since I've done something like this. Gotten a bit rusty.","quest_name":"What Burns Beneath Frostlands","quest_id":915000004},{"text":"Stay in your comfort zone too long and you start to slack off without realizing it... Back in the day, I would've handled this in 28 seconds flat.","quest_name":"What Burns Beneath Frostlands","quest_id":915000004},{"text":"Because… the longest reboot time for the Auto-Defense Array is 28 seconds.","quest_name":"What Burns Beneath Frostlands","quest_id":915000004},{"text":"...You think?","quest_name":"What Burns Beneath Frostlands","quest_id":915000004},{"text":"Ahem... sorry, back to the topic. While digging through the database, I noticed something.","quest_name":"What Burns Beneath Frostlands","quest_id":915000004},{"text":"The Academy's mechs and the <te href=700014>Voidmatter Barrier</te> security logs show unusual access. Someone used admin-level protocols.","quest_name":"What Burns Beneath Frostlands","quest_id":915000004},{"text":"Also, the device's data has three frequency waveforms. One from Hyvatia. The other two are... unrecognizable.","quest_name":"What Burns Beneath Frostlands","quest_id":915000004},{"text":"Um... Heh, just by, uh... browsing the Academy Forum.","quest_name":"What Burns Beneath Frostlands","quest_id":915000004},{"text":"Mm, alright, I was once tasked to hack into the Institute's database and tamper with Hyvatia's calibration data.","quest_name":"What Burns Beneath Frostlands","quest_id":915000004},{"text":"But I didn't change anything. Just threw in a few emojis and left a note telling them to upgrade their encryption.","quest_name":"What Burns Beneath Frostlands","quest_id":915000004},{"text":"That backfired though. Got me flagged.","quest_name":"What Burns Beneath Frostlands","quest_id":915000004},{"text":"I think you're right. Next, we need to figure out what those waveforms correspond to. Maybe we'll find a clue in the Lahai-Roi ecological studies.","quest_name":"What Burns Beneath Frostlands","quest_id":915000004},{"text":"Let's head to the Spacetrek Archive then.","quest_name":"What Burns Beneath Frostlands","quest_id":915000004},{"text":"Ahem, allow me to introduce Miss I.R.I.S. She's—","quest_name":"What Burns Beneath Frostlands","quest_id":915000004},{"text":"That's right! She's the Archive's administrator, responsible for indexing all the data here. A very reliable senior, you could say.","quest_name":"What Burns Beneath Frostlands","quest_id":915000004},{"text":"You look beat. Everything okay, Miss I.R.I.S.?","quest_name":"What Burns Beneath Frostlands","quest_id":915000004},{"text":"We want to look up info related to this waveform data.","quest_name":"What Burns Beneath Frostlands","quest_id":915000004},{"text":"That's a lot… Add these keywords: \"Void Storm\" and \"Exoswarm Contamination.\"","quest_name":"What Burns Beneath Frostlands","quest_id":915000004},{"text":"A big improvement. Let's split up and review them.","quest_name":"What Burns Beneath Frostlands","quest_id":915000004},{"text":"Whew… the Academy is safe. Thank goodness.","quest_name":"What Burns Beneath Frostlands","quest_id":915000004},{"text":"Whoa... so many people here.","quest_name":"What Burns Beneath Frostlands","quest_id":915000004},{"text":"Dark... Thunderbolt?","quest_name":"What Burns Beneath Frostlands","quest_id":915000004},{"text":"...","quest_name":"What Burns Beneath Frostlands","quest_id":915000004},{"text":"Sorry, guys. I need to report the Voidworm incident to the Academy first.","quest_name":"What Burns Beneath Frostlands","quest_id":915000004},{"text":"Once that's done, I'll tell you everything you want to know. Promise.","quest_name":"What Burns Beneath Frostlands","quest_id":915000004},{"text":"I do. I'm not a Startorch student anymore. Rules are rules, and I should return to the New Federation.","quest_name":"What Burns Beneath Frostlands","quest_id":915000004},{"text":"That's it, right?","quest_name":"What Burns Beneath Frostlands","quest_id":915000004},{"text":"Yeah. I know.","quest_name":"What Burns Beneath Frostlands","quest_id":915000004},{"text":"What?","quest_name":"What Burns Beneath Frostlands","quest_id":915000004},{"text":"An inquiry? Sure. And the entrance exam? No problem.","quest_name":"What Burns Beneath Frostlands","quest_id":915000004},{"text":"Thank you.","quest_name":"What Burns Beneath Frostlands","quest_id":915000004},{"text":"Yeah, see you!","quest_name":"What Burns Beneath Frostlands","quest_id":915000004},{"text":"Gosh. Never thought I'd be this happy to take a freaking exam.","quest_name":"What Burns Beneath Frostlands","quest_id":915000004},{"text":"The Academy convenience store's specials are really good.","quest_name":"What Burns Beneath Frostlands","quest_id":915000004},{"text":"When I become a \"freshman\" at Startorch, let's go grab a bite together, okay?","quest_name":"What Burns Beneath Frostlands","quest_id":915000004},{"text":"You want me to testify against Professor Warren? That's practically perjury… Sure, I could work some verbal magic, but honestly, I don't even know who I'm dealing with on the other side...","quest_name":"Ode to the Second Sunrise","quest_id":936000002},{"text":"Professor Mornye...","quest_name":"Ode to the Second Sunrise","quest_id":936000002},{"text":"—Nice working with you, then.","quest_name":"Ode to the Second Sunrise","quest_id":936000002}]}